Tags : earthquakes in India , earthquake in northeast , earthquake in Sikkim , Mangan and Singhtam areas Sikkim , Sikkim earthquake epicentre , landslides in Sikkim , rescue operations in sikkim , earthquake epicentre out of reach India is not prepared for high - intensity earthquakes , says experts 21 Sep 2011 Pointing to an increase in tectonic activities that escalate the chances of more earthquakes in India , experts say the country ' s preparedness to deal with the disasters seems to be missing .